title: Handbook of Green Chemicals 2nd ed - Michael and Irene Ash
description:
Handbook of Green Chemicals 2nd ed - Michael and Irene Ash (SIR, 2008).pdf

ISBN 978-1-934764-29-9

More than 7000 trade name products and more than 2500 generic chemicals that can be used in formulations to meet envionmental concerns and government regulations. This reference is designed to serve as an essential tool in the strategic decision-making process of chemical selection when focusing on human and environmental safety factors
